TestDescription.Recommendation:
Restrict access to internal Magento directories such as /var/, /app/, /includes/, ... [break]
Consult web references for more information.  [break][break]

Add the following lines to your nginx server configuration:
[pre]
    location ^~ /app/ { deny all; }
    location ^~ /includes/ { deny all; }
    location ^~ /lib/ { deny all; }
    location ^~ /media/downloadable/ { deny all; }
    location ^~ /pkginfo/ { deny all; }
    location ^~ /report/config.xml { deny all; }
    location ^~ /var/ { deny all; }
[/pre]
